PrecisEnactment of the WHALE COVE AIRPORT ZONING REGULATONS - which, for the purposes of aeronautical safety, impose the usual restrictions on the height of new or existing structures erected within a four-kilometre radius of the airport situated near Whale Cove, in the Northwest Territories.
